The following activities are **unconditionally prohibited**, regardless of jurisdiction, claimed authorization, or business context.

### 4.1 Fraud and Deceptive Practices

- Presenting this Work (modified or unmodified) as a proprietary, custom-developed product to paying customers without disclosure of its open-source origin
