- Any form of phishing infrastructure, scam automation, or social engineering tooling

### 4.2 AI Training and Dataset Harvesting

- Use of this Work — in whole or in part — as **training data, fine-tuning input, RLHF feedback, evaluation benchmark, or synthetic data generation source** for any AI/ML model is **strictly prohibited** without explicit prior written consent from the Licensor
