### 4.3 Closed-Source AI Commercialization

- Integration of this Work into any Closed AI System where the Work contributes to a product that restricts user access, generates revenue, or reduces the openness of the AI ecosystem, is prohibited without a separate commercial license agreement with the Licensor
- This includes indirect incorporation: using this Work to generate outputs that are then used as training data for closed models is a violation of Section 4.2 and this section

### 4.4 Weapons, Military, and Lethal Systems

The Work shall **never** be used in:

- Development, testing, optimization, simulation, or deployment of autonomous weapons systems or lethal autonomous systems (LAWS)
