- Military targeting, fire-control, surveillance, or combat decision-support systems
- Export-controlled weapons technology subject to ITAR, EAR, or equivalent national regulations
- Any system whose primary designed purpose is to cause physical harm to human beings

This prohibition applies regardless of the claimed legality of the weapons program under any national or international law.

### 4.5 Unauthorized Security Operations

